name: UDJ01AbilitySet
doc:
UDJ01AbilitySet

     Non-mutable data asset used to grant gameplay abilities and gameplay effects.

GrantedGameplayAbilities: Gameplay abilities to grant when this ability set is granted.
GrantedGameplayEffects: Gameplay effects to grant when this ability set is granted.
GrantedAttributes: Attribute sets to grant when this ability set is granted.
